; Coverage test for journal.cc line 213
; Tests infinite alias recursion detection for partial (first-account) aliases.
; When --recursive-aliases is enabled and alias A->B and B->A exist,
; expanding "A:Sub" finds A->B, then B->A, detecting the cycle.

alias A=B
alias B=A

2024/01/15 Test
    A:Sub             $50.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal --recursive-aliases -> 1
__ERROR__
While parsing file "$FILE", line 10:
While parsing posting:
  A:Sub             $50.00

Error: Infinite recursion on alias expansion for A
end test
